              <header class="style1">
                <h2>What is JamWatHQ?</h2>
              </header>
              <p>
                Welcome to JamWatHQ, your one-stop hub for reliable information tailored specifically to Jamaican J1
                students. We are here to help you confidently navigate your work and travel journey while staying
                connected to your roots.
              </p>

              <p>
                At JamWatHQ, we offer a wealth of carefully curated resources designed to empower you at every step. For
                example, our comprehensive agency information provides a detailed list of approved agencies and
                sponsors, complete with rankings to help you choose trusted partners as you embark on your adventure. In
                addition, our platform keeps you informed with the latest news and alerts related to the J1 program,
                including up-to-date scam alerts and safety notifications that ensure you remain well-protected.
              </p>

              <p>
                We also make it easy to access essential embassy resources. With just a few clicks, you can reach key
                sites such as the visa application portal, I-94 details, and the DHS I-901 website, ensuring that all
                the official tools you need are at your fingertips. Moreover, our practical guidance section offers
                extensive FAQs, general work and travel insights, and advice on which jobs to so that you can make
                informed decisions every step of the way.
              </p>

              <p>
                Our goal is clear: to provide concise, straightforward guidance that enables you to navigate your J1
                experience with unwavering confidence, safety, and a profound connection to your Jamaican heritage. At
                JamWatHQ, you're not just informed—you're empowered to take on the world.
              </p>

              <header class="style1">
                <h2>Who we are not!</h2>
              </header>

              <p>
                At Jamwathq, we want to be clear that we are solely an information hub for the J1 program. We are not an
                agency, a sponsor, a recruiter, or a host employer, nor do we serve as a representative or consultant of
                any kind. We also do not operate a WhatsApp group or any similar channel. Our purpose is to provide
                reliable and straightforward information to help you safely navigate the complexities of the J1
                experience. If you encounter anyone claiming to be an official Jamwathq agent, please report that
                individual to the police immediately.
              </p>
